events.description:
@bethanie8, setbacks are natural. Please be kind to yourself. IIH UK have a series of specially developed exercises for people with IIH on YouTube that you might find useful. They are not Yoga, but do take into account many of the struggles sufferers face. 

https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCEpwmN0MWtQ-6hRSL4A1Vpw 

I'm not certain if the link will work here. It is shared later in the programme, but I will share it in the newsfeed today

